Package io.toolisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.tools.corematcher Description

This package contains the implementation classes for the different kinds of CoreMatchers. Currently there are the following CoreMatcher types: - Implicit matchers (no arguments) - Is matcher (no arguments like implicit matcher, but changes element type) - Characteristic matchers --> Inclusive matchers (Matcher none, one, at least one or all characteristics) --> Exclusive matchers (Matches none or one characteristic)
